# Power BI MCP Server — Phase 2 credentials
# Step 1: Go to https://portal.azure.com
# Step 2: Azure Active Directory > App registrations > New registration
# Step 3: Add API permissions: Power BI Service > Delegated > Report.Read.All, Dataset.Read.All
# Step 4: Create a client secret under Certificates & secrets
# Step 5: Fill in the values below and rename this file to .env

PBI_TENANT_ID=your-tenant-id-here
PBI_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here
PBI_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here
PBI_USERNAME=your-powerbi-email@domain.com
PBI_PASSWORD=your-powerbi-password